### What these diagrams deliberately do *not* show

- **What other aggregates do during a transition** — see Golden-path
  Sequence diagrams (`<NN>-golden-path-*.md`) if Tier-3 was generated.
- **The events emitted on transition** — see Event Ribbon
  (`<NN>-event-ribbon.md`) for the chronological event view.
- **Cross-aggregate consistency** — DDD aggregates are individually
  consistent; cross-aggregate consistency is eventual and lives in the
  Context Map (`<NN>-bounded-context-map.md`).

