## Legend

| Notation | Meaning |
|----------|---------|
| `[*] -->` | Initial state (aggregate creation) |
| `--> [*]` | Terminal state (aggregate settled) |
| `A --> B: cmd` | Transition triggered by command/event `cmd` |
| `[guard]` | Guard condition; transition fires only if guard true |

